  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore mouse-infested dream worlds as a cat! Grow magical catnip to gain powerful abilities, reclaim stolen furniture, and expand your ever-growing catnip farm. Reminiscent of Goat Simulator, Catniptic delivers chaotic, quirky fun! This psychedelic platformer never plays the same twice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/5df8f1409383198d553ddbe7e55cbdd4.poster.avif?t=1727490253\" width=680 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/5df8f1409383198d553ddbe7e55cbdd4.webm?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/5df8f1409383198d553ddbe7e55cbdd4.mp4?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/221f951da86cb385437f77b80d5b6caa.avif?t=1727490253\" width=680 height=100 /></span>Step into the paws of a feline protagonist and unlock a range of ludicrous abilities! As you grow and harvest magical catnip, you'll discover jump boosts, lasers to zap foes, explosive attacks, and the unparalleled skill of walking on two legs. Unravel each dream's unique theme, complete with distinct landscapes and hidden features that offer intricate paths to navigate. Among these dream worlds lie pots of catnip and friendly cats trading catnip seeds. Seeds and treasured items can be yours for the right price in coins earned from vanquishing mice. Traverse treacherous platforms, maintain your ever-growing catnip farm, and uncover dormant secrets within each dream's narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/9bc4ca13e825f8ffe2481988b0e6a24d.avif?t=1727490253\" width=680 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/247027df0f1b8a9b284c36f8591c2be6.avif?t=1727490253\" width=676 height=516 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/1cab4bdfc04e055fd1539caa0ac6067d.poster.avif?t=1727490253\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/1cab4bdfc04e055fd1539caa0ac6067d.webm?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/1cab4bdfc04e055fd1539caa0ac6067d.mp4?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/6cf1c52741bbf238d8de51dadf7e39c3.poster.avif?t=1727490253\" width=800 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/6cf1c52741bbf238d8de51dadf7e39c3.webm?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/6cf1c52741bbf238d8de51dadf7e39c3.mp4?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/7a7078db28b88c4250e27e957f4e0a43.poster.avif?t=1727490253\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/7a7078db28b88c4250e27e957f4e0a43.webm?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/7a7078db28b88c4250e27e957f4e0a43.mp4?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/33b981a394c6afbc37d1861abf6cb7e8.poster.avif?t=1727490253\" width=800 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/33b981a394c6afbc37d1861abf6cb7e8.webm?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/33b981a394c6afbc37d1861abf6cb7e8.mp4?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore mouse-infested dream worlds as a cat! Grow magical catnip to gain powerful abilities, reclaim stolen furniture, and expand your ever-growing catnip farm. Reminiscent of Goat Simulator, Catniptic delivers chaotic, quirky fun! This psychedelic platformer never plays the same twice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/5df8f1409383198d553ddbe7e55cbdd4.poster.avif?t=1727490253\" width=680 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/5df8f1409383198d553ddbe7e55cbdd4.webm?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/5df8f1409383198d553ddbe7e55cbdd4.mp4?t=1727490253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2507130/extras/221f951da86cb385437f77b80d5b6caa.avif?t=1727490253\" width=680 height=100 /></span>Step into the paws of a feline protagonist and unlock a range of ludicrous abilities! As you grow and harvest magical catnip, you'll discover jump boosts, lasers to zap foes, explosive attacks, and the unparalleled skill of walking on two legs. Unravel each dream's unique theme, complete with distinct landscapes and hidden features that offer intricate paths to navigate. Among these dream worlds lie pots of catnip and friendly cats trading catnip seeds. Seeds and treasured items can be yours for the right price in coins earned from vanquishing mice. Traverse treacherous platforms, maintain your ever-growing catnip farm, and uncover dormant secrets within each dream's narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=